I"≠Ú<p>In this project, we‚Äôre going to build a simple recurrent neural network from scratch, using NumPy.</p>

<p>We‚Äôll add a fun twist to this project by training the RNN on a dataset containing song lyrics by Justin Bieber, and we‚Äôll see how well it can generate new lyrics based on the learned patterns!</p>

<p>Given the foundational knowledge on neural networks established in previous projects, we‚Äôll move relatively quickly into the theory for RNNs.</p>

<p>This project is also closely linked to the next one on Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) networks, where we will improve on the RNN architecture.</p>

<p>Here‚Äôs the structure for this project post:</p>

<p>1. Recurrent Neural Network Overview</p>

<p>2. Describing the RNN mathematically</p>

<p>2.1 Forward Propagation</p>

<p>2.2 Backward Propagation</p>

