\boxed{\frac{‚àÇ L^{&lt;t&gt;}}{‚àÇ W_{hh}} = \frac{‚àÇ L^{&lt;t&gt;}}{‚àÇ z_h^{&lt;t&gt;}} \cdot \frac{‚àÇ z_h^{&lt;t&gt;}}{‚àÇ W_{hh}} = \frac{‚àÇ L^{&lt;t&gt;}}{‚àÇ z_h^{&lt;t&gt;}} \cdot \frac{‚àÇ (W_{hx} x^{&lt;t&gt;} + W_{hh} h^{&lt;t-1&gt;} + b_h)}{‚àÇ W_{hh}} = \frac{‚àÇ L^{&lt;t&gt;}}{‚àÇ z_h^{&lt;t&gt;}} \cdot h^{&lt;t-1&gt;}}
